<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，汤姆去参加野餐了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没带猫咪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆想玩儿游戏，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他还是很担心德克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿了一些吃的坐下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，有人坐在他旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是安！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆吓得扔掉了盘子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说你在找我。”安说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我昨天去魔法师学校了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆把掉的东西捡起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“德克为什么那么讨厌我？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>安看上去很难过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我父亲是大管家。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，皇家魔法师的权力要大得多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这让我的父亲很烦恼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有大麻烦了。”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉了安猫咪的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“德克要把猫的事情告诉所有人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“父亲也不喜欢上一任皇家魔法师。”安说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个魔法师对父亲施了个坏魔法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让他身上有猫味儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，父亲也让王后打喷嚏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“后来，国王知道了这件事。”安说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他就开除了皇家魔法师。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也会被开除的。”汤姆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果德克告诉了国王，那么......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>安突然站了起来，抓住了汤姆的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我刚想起一件事！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟我来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
